it.mdx#method-declaration\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nasync def deposit(\\n    self, wallet: Wallet, address: str, subaccount_number: int, amount: Decimal\\n) -&gt; Anyasync depositToMegavault(\\n    subaccount: SubaccountInfo,\\n    amountUsdc: number,\\n    broadcastMode?: BroadcastMode,\\n): Promise&lt;BroadcastTxAsyncResponse | BroadcastTxSyncResponse | IndexedTx&gt;pub async fn deposit_to_megavault(\\n    &amp;mut self,\\n    account: &amp;mut Account,\\n    subaccount: Subaccount,\\n    amount: impl Into&lt;Usdc&gt;,\\n) -&gt; Result&lt;TxHash, NodeError&gt;\\nUnification Plan\\n\",\"title\":\"Method Declaration\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Deposit to MegaVault\"]},{\"href\":\"/node-client/private/megavault/deposit#parameters\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Location</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>account</code></td><td>query</td><td><a href=\\\"/types/account\\\">Account</a></td><td>Owner&#x27;s account information</td></tr><tr><td><code>subaccount</code></td><td>query</td><td><a href=\\\"/types/subaccount_info\\\">SubaccountInfo</a></td><td>Subaccount information</td></tr><tr><td><code>amount</code></td><td>query</td><td>Decimal</td><td>Amount in usdc to deposit</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/private/megavault/deposit.mdx#parameters\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nParameterLocationTypeDescriptionaccountqueryAccountOwner&#x27;s account informationsubaccountquerySubaccountInfoSubaccount informationamountqueryDecimalAmount in usdc to deposit\\n\",\"title\":\"Parameters\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Deposit to MegaVault\"]},{\"href\":\"/node-client/private/megavault/deposit#response\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Schema</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>200</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/ok\\\">OK</a></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/tx_hash\\\">TxHash</a></td><td>The transaction hash.</td></tr><tr><td><code>400